Package tiralabra.gui.geometrytools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildGraph
    Mouse input tool that lets user position vertices and build the graph freely by connecting vertices by hand.
    ChainPolygon
    Mouse input tool that lets user chain points together to form polygons.
    FreeDraw
    Tool that lets user form polygons as if user used a thick brush to draw shapes.
    InsertPoint
    Tool for inserting a point between two points.
    JoinPolygons
    Tool for joining two separate polygons.
    MoveOrDeletePoint
    Tool for moving or deleting a point of a polygon.
    MoveOrDeletePolygon
    Tool for moving or deleting entire polygons.
    SetEndPoints
    Sets A and B points for building the shortest path between them.
    ShowUnobstructed
    Trace mode.
